{"tid":1031310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【火雞姐終現身】仲未賠錢畀被欺凌同學？ 丁可欣：總之有聯絡過","createTime":"2019-02-21T14:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T06:21:38.000Z","uid":162183,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1da16896d5b9bb18f93ad45c53e9b7a4f7217086","tid":1031310,"uid":162183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"丁可欣早前被網民爆中學時代欺凌同學，以及偷同學錢和電話，其後丁可欣拍片向曾經被欺凌的同學道歉，更指會向有關同學賠償。今天她出席《恭喜八婆》慶功宴時被問起此事，她的反應很避忌，還強調：「我要講嘅嘢喺條片講咗喇，嚟緊自己會努力向自己嘅目標進發。」問到在拍道歉片前有沒有和公司商量過才拍，丁可欣指：「我自己獨立嘅，不過有經理人，都有商量過，我要講嘅嘢已經喺條片交待晒。」問到最近的工作有否因此事而受到影響，她指沒有，但這一刻需要時間迎接挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n再追問丁可欣到現時賠了多少錢給涉事同學，她沒有正面回答，只答：「聯絡咗幾位相關嘅同學。」問到對方有沒有接受道歉，她支支吾吾地答：「總之有聯絡過，對方都有接受，嚟緊會努力做要面對嘅事。」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWNFXhQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWNFXhQ.jpg&h=4cf67159&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://whyhow.info/6710/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhyhow.info%2F6710%2F&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=d980ae6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://whyhow.info/6710/</a>"},{"pid":"3d458bec9e122e0feda23bba315c9cd0c9af53f8","tid":1031310,"uid":210522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:27:04.000Z","msg":"一出道就搞d咁既野 老細實激死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15998c9a23b5c9cb72cdaa76a319ddab4f61e73","tid":1031310,"uid":191047,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:29:20.000Z","msg":"比記者問到口啞啞<br />\n仲要啲記者問到想屌鳩佢 笑撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b047cbf877b32ab95e5f1e3fccfa79b83b27a4d","tid":1031310,"uid":191047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T14:40:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"ht